data.description: Welcome to maintenance free lake living! 34732 E Lake is located just steps from all sports Lake St Clair. This well maintained 2 bedroom, 1.5 bath town house with attached garage sits on the edge of the complex providing lake views from every window! With approximately 1200 square feet of finished space , this home features a cozy fireplace for those cool evenings you're not enjoying the lake, a Master Bedroom with an expansive walk in closet, , and lastly- fresh paint throughout the 1st floor. A brand new sea wall makes this property a must see. Come explore the hassle free Lake Life this home has to offer.
